## How to Use These Templates

Placeholders you need to replace:

- `<YOUR-APP-NAME>` -- your application name
- `<YOUR-NAMESPACE>` -- pai-dev, pai-test, or pai-prod
- `<YOUR-PORT>` -- the port your app listens on
- `<YOUR-HOSTNAME>` -- FQDN for your service

Do not modify anything outside the placeholders unless instructed. The annotations, labels, and references are pre-configured for the OCP-AI platform.

